§§ Notation ⦉
¶ ⦊
  ‖ We denote the product $p_m(n)$ by $m · n$. ⦉

  ‖ We often drop the $·$ and write $m · n$ as $mn$. ⦉
⦉

<!--
 two numbers by $m + n$.
 We denote the function addition by $+$
 and so denote the sum of the naturals
 $m$ and $n$ by $m + n$.
-->

